eu.smartdatalake.simsearch.ranking

Class RankedResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.smartdatalake.simsearch.ranking.RankedResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IResult

    public class RankedResult
extends Object
implements IResult
    Auxiliary class that is used to collect the attribute values and their scores for a final result, along with its ranking and aggregate score.
